content: Calibel's Mine is an easy dungeon with , and Bandits, giving you a good way to farm this monster family. Overall this aspect and dungeon aren't too valuable, and you should only do this dungeon once for the Renown completion. This map will help you identify those layouts so you can complete dungeons faster and maximize your XP and loot per hour! Reviewed by
